                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The behir breathes lightning that deals [[/r 9d6 #electricity]]{9d6 electricity damage} in an 60-foot line (<span data-pf2-check=\"reflex\" data-pf2-dc=\"27\" data-pf2-traits=\"electricity,evocation,primal,damaging-effect\" data-pf2-label=\"Breath Weapon DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">basic Reflex</span> save).</p>\n<p>It can't use Breath Weapon again for [[/br 1d4 #rounds]]{1d4 rounds}.</p>"
