                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> The behir has a creature either @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Restrained]{Restrained} or @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Grabbed]{Grabbed} in its jaws;</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The behir moves the creature into its coils, freeing its jaws. The creature remains grabbed and takes [[/r 1d6+6 #slashing]]{1d6+6 slashing damage}. The behir's coils can hold as many creatures as will fit in its space.</p>"
